Package com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.core.concurrency.capsules

Interface Summary
ICapsule  
 

Class Summary
AbstractCapsule Capsules represent autonomous units of functionality within the KeYTestGen2 core, meant to make it easy for the system as a whole to run concurrently.
CapsuleController<T extends ICapsule>  
CapsuleExecutor Encapsulates an Executor for global use across KeYTestGen2.
ClassCapsule  
LaunchContainer  
MethodCapsule Instances of this capsule enables KeYTestGen2 to concurrently generate test suites for multiple Java methods.
ModelCapsule Instances of this class are used in order to enable concurrent model generation for several nodes simultaneously.
OracleCapsule Instances of this capsule enables KeYTestGen2 to to concurrently generate oracles for multiple methods.
